üé¨ Prompt Title: Depth to Infinity ‚Äî 3D Cinematic Portfolio

Core Identity:

> A GPU-optimized, cinematic, and interactive 3D portfolio that flows from ocean to space ‚Äî projects as living planets, blog as glowing stars, and contact as an orbiting signal composer. Built for modern browsers, optimized for performance, and responsive across all devices.




---

‚öôÔ∏è Tech Stack & Setup

Frontend: React + Three.js (via React Three Fiber) + Framer Motion + Tailwind CSS + MUI

Backend: Laravel API (for blog, contact, and admin)

Renderer: WebGL2 with post-processing (bloom, godrays, chromatic aberration)

Performance: GPU instancing, lazy loading, LOD models, shader compression, async texture load

Accessibility: ARIA labels, reduced motion toggle, keyboard nav

Modes: Light/Dark palette (user-defined)

Audio: Toggle top-right corner; subtle ambient + reactive sounds


